-- Kofi Annan Resigns as UN Syria Envoy After Peace Efforts Failed
-- B y   F l a v i a   K r a u s e - J a c k s o n
-- 2012-08-02T14:53:58Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-02/kofi-annan-resigns-as-un-syria-envoy-after-peace-efforts-failed.html
Kofi Annan , the United Nations
special envoy to Syria, today resigned after failing in his
peace efforts to end the 17-month crisis.  His resignation was announced in a statement distributed by
the UN via e-mail.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Flavia Krause-Jackson at 
 fjackson@bloomberg.net  